Package: arschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Arkansas School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Arkansas Department of
    Education (ADE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from the
    ADE Data Center and Annual Statistical Reports, then transforming it into
    tidy format for analysis. Supports historical data from 2005 to present.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readxl,
    readr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    httr,
    rappdirs,
    rvest
